data.description: Start the new year off right in your new home!! These sellers have gone above and beyond with numerous updates, making this home an incredible value.  A new roof was installed earlier this year and the kitchen has undergone a stunning transformation with a complete kitchen remodel. Enjoy new ceramic tile flooring, brand new white cabinets, sleek quartz countertops with a stylish backsplash and additional cabinets with bamboo countertops providing ample storage space.  The attention to detail is evident with new crown molding and beautifully reframed doorways, along with brand new interior doors for all bedrooms, enhancing the overall aesthetics of the home.  Say goodbye to carpet hassles and allergies!! This home features durable and water resistant laminate, vinyl plank in addition to the ceramic tile we mentioned before. A spacious bonus room at the rear of the home offers versatile options for entertainment, a home office or play area.  And if you???re a fan of billiards, the pool table can convey for the right offer.  But wait, there???s more!  A new roof has been installed this year, plus the back yard is designed for enjoyment and relaxation. A recently added patio slab will make relaxing on the back porch even more enjoyable. This home offers convenience to local amenities, schools and recreational facilities. Don???t wait to schedule your showing because in this price range, it should sell quickly. 2023-11-27
